{"title":"呵，廉政……","authors":["易仁寰"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":9,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，廉政……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"易仁寰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以你作匾，装潢过多少朝廷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你当歌，礼赞过多少衙门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于你不甘粉饰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于你披满征尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从《甲申三百年祭》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌的大厅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你曾“露宿街头”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谱写过南京路上的党颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那人欲横流的市井"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未曾染污你金色的权柄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当糖弹像飞蛾般扑来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你亮起《准则》的明灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了不使被砸碎的镣铐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重新铸就金子的锁链"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你千百次呼唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霓虹灯下的哨兵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用你净化的执政"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能托起公仆的责任"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以你校正的法律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在瞄准"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"膨胀的贪心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，廉政——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是杨靖宇腹中的野草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是方志敏腰包的清贫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是周恩来补丁层层的衬衣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是焦裕禄扎根兰考的赤诚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，廉政——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不是写在蓝天上的宣言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只是刻在大地上的脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，在商品角逐的闹市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在八方洞开的国门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿你化作新华门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不倒的旗杆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和纪念碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声的叮咛……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}